## User / Author is a Stripe Connect vendor condition

**User is a Stripe Connect vendor condition**Â condition checks if the current user has finished [Stripe onboarding](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_stripe-connect_.md) to become a vendor

While **Author is a Stripe Connect vendor condition** checks if the current post author has finished onboarding to become a vendor

## Example

You can use this condition for example to Restrict users who are not vendors from creating products, or seeing product related features such as sale stats
